About Me

I am currently a PhD student in School of Data Science, Fudan University, under the advised of Prof. Xuening Zhu. I obtained my Bachelor’s Degree in Economics and Master’s Degree in Applied Statistics from School of Statistics, Renmin University of China. My research interest lies in Network Analysis, High-dimensional Statistics, and Graph Neural Network.
